    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Someone makes an ambiguous request.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "You assume you know what they want.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "They become upset when what they get isn't what they wanted.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Clarifying questions are a great way to avoid the conflict that comes when you miss the mark by relying on an inaccurate map.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "In fact, compared to the turmoil of creating something only to go back and redo it, asking questions ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "just to be clear",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " is infinitely worth more than ‘inconveniencing someone.’",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "They’re also free.",
          "marks": []
        }
